Hello, this is my first comment
I wanted to say this upload works 100%, the dispatch works flawlessly and I'm enjoying REALLY fast internet.
So this is how I got it to work if it didn't for some people, I installed the program, blocked all the .exe files in the directory (in program files/connectify) through a firewall (I recommend Windows Firewall Control) and then opened the program and registered, that's it.
If you tried the serial before and it blocked you I recommend uninstalling with total uninstall or revo uninstaller and re-trying again.
Oh I forgot to say, this is the final version but DO NOT UPDATE when asked.
tnx a lot hope to boost up my net
